import React from 'react'
import { Button, Card, Container, Row, ListGroup, Col, Form } from 'react-bootstrap';

const BuyToken = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Card>
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Header> Buying coins </Card.Header>
                        <Form>
                            <Form.Group controlId="formBasicEmail">
                                <Form.Label>Enter name of the token</Form.Label>
                                <Form.Control type="token" placeholder="TokenIndetfier" />
                            </Form.Group>
                        </Form>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
};

export default BuyToken
